合约接口调用。    Parameters   Object - The transaction call object  from: DATA, 20 Bytes - (optional) The address the transaction is sent from.  to:   DATA, 20 Bytes - The address the transaction is directed to.  data: DATA - (optional) Hash of the method signature and encoded parameters. For details see  Ethereum Contract ABI    QUANTITY - block parameter  HEX String - an integer block number  String "earliest" for the earliest/genesis block  String "latest" - for the latest mined block     params :   [{ "from" : "0xca35b7d915458ef540ade6068dfe2f44e8fa733c" , "to" : "0xea4f6bc98b456ef085da5c424db710489848cab5" , "data" : "0x6d4ce63c" },   "0x1d23" ]     Returns  DATA , 32 Bytes - the transaction hash.    Example  contract中get方法Hash和编码后的数据  0x6d4ce63c    发送和获取数据  // Request
